Sorry Yanshosh.  And yes, it sounded feminine and threw me off.
My appologies.

:Feline:
She started walking with Reptilica.  She then felt a sharp pain in 
her neck. "OUCH!" The electric charge surdged through her body and 
she fell to the ground unconsious.


--- In nbwrpg@egroups.com, Yanshosh@a... wrote:
> Reptilica is a male, Logo. The name might sound feminine, but I 
didn't name 
> him.
> 
> ::Reptilica/DevilDuer::
> 
> Reptilica nods. "Follow me," he says, walking off toward the 
Alliance base.
> ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
> In the bushes, DevilDuer narrows his eyes, carefully aiming his gun 
at 
> Feline's head. He fires a stun dart, the shot heading for the 
female's neck. 
> If it hits, it would send electric waves through the bot, rendering 
it 
> unconscious for several hours.
